            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> dill </strong>and<strong> chives</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Toss the <strong>salad </strong>in the <strong>zingy dressing</strong>, then set this aside until serving – this is your<strong> zingy salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/907__-step-4-x200.jpg",
