          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/907.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze in the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> and add <strong>half </strong>of your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later) with<strong> half</strong> the<strong> chopped dill </strong>and<strong> chives</strong> (save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>smoked mackerel linguine</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
